      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "aClass",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The class for which to return a class description. See note below for important details."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The class description for "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "aClass"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", or "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if a class description cannot be found."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If a class description for "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "aClass"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is not found, the method posts an NSClassDescriptionNeededForClassNotification on behalf of "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "aClass"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", allowing an observer to register a class description. The method then checks for a class description again. Returns "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " if a class description is still not found."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you have an instance of the receiver’s class, you can use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NSObject"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance method "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/nsobject/1411858-classdescription"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "In macOS 10.6 and later, this method (and as a result "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/nsobject/1411858-classdescription"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " methods of any object) will return "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "nil"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " when the sdef contains no "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "<class>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " element for the Cocoa class, but there is a "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "<class>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " element defined for a superclass."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "This is incorrect, as object instances should never be required to be exactly a given class, any class should be allowed to be a subclass of the required class and receive the correct "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "<class>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " value."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "This situation can have a serious impact on Cocoa Scripting, and there is no plan on changing this behavior."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Instead of using this method, you should use the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsscriptclassdescription/1414196-classdescriptionforclass"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " method of "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsscriptclassdescription"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " instead."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "note",
          "name": "Note"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
